flowchart LR
    subgraph live [Live Path]
        LiveFeed[Broker WebSocket]
        LiveNorm[Adapter Normalizer]
        LiveBus[EventBus]
        LiveOMS[OrderManager PositionManager]
    end

    subgraph seam [MarketDataSource Port]
        MDS[subscribe emit Quote TICK]
    end

    subgraph replay [Replay Path]
        Parquet[Parquet bars ticks]
        ReplayNorm[Same Normalizer]
        ReplayBus[Same EventBus]
        ReplayOMS[Same PositionManager]
    end

    LiveFeed --> LiveNorm
    LiveNorm --> MDS
    MDS --> LiveBus
    LiveBus --> LiveOMS

    Parquet --> ReplayNorm
    ReplayNorm --> MDS
    MDS --> ReplayBus
    ReplayBus --> ReplayOMS

    Note[Zero parity rule same objects same subscribers]
